Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about a year ago when we\Nhad our entrance ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:09.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Class 1-A" "Class 1-B"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Our class assignments were stuck\Nto the bulletin boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And among the crowd of new students,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,there was one other girl keeping her distance\Nfrom the crowd, just like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who exchanged glances with me then\Njust happened to be Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, back then, I had\Nabsolutely no interest in strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I even hoped that she'd stop looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A year had passed, and now, Shimamura\Nand I were both second-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Does God actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something that could\Nhear my voiceless prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class again.\NHow many years has it been now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:55.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Class 3-E" "Class 2-A" "Class 2-B" "Class 2-C"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like almost everyone else\Ngot split up. Like Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If we end up in separate classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura probably wouldn't come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably wouldn't mind\Nif I came to see her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But she wouldn't come to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't think Shimamura\Nactually needs me that badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:20.45,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Class 2-B" "Sakura Adachi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm definitely not a decent\Nperson worth any praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine that I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,enough good deeds to be\Nrewarded with anything I ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Does God actually exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something that could\Nhear my voiceless prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:43.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Sakura Adachi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish and I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I stand tall, searching for that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.98,0:01:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yippee! Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:08.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Hogetsu Shimamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I started my second year in high school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and my hair color went\Nback to its natural color.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In my new class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,my seat and most of my classmates had changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but Adachi still remained right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So your first name is Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever ask you that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you prefer Miss Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I mean... Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I was just looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi... Why are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, that's what you meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so much like a puppy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll go get my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually like dogs quite a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never get over how big her house is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll, roll, roll, roll, roll, roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll, roll, roll, roll, roll, roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the tatami is just so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I changed, just like you asked.\NThis is what you wanted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute, Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first thought to cross my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. I guess I'll get changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to spend the night\Nat your place today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your place is huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured no one would notice\Neven if I stayed over. Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously... You should've asked me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'd object if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Tae, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I sure am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, your name is Taeko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're already changed.\NPlease come greet our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why do I have to greet them, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a part of this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is exactly why\NI hate coming home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Shimamura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Hey, wanna have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, come on. Come sit with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come this way, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:08:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't bring my lunch,\Nso I'm going to go buy something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So have you guys been friends for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, just since this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in any clubs, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in concert band.\NThe number of members is a bit iffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They all introduced themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but they talked too fast\Nand I couldn't understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was something like\NPancho, Sancho, and Delos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured they must be some kind\Nof traveling comedy troupe. JK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that those\Nwere actually their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, their idle chatter continued, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to remember what they\Nwere talking about, but just couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the caf√© by the station now.\NWant to come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Their pancakes are super yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a cute little shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, uh... Sorry, I can't today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Our classes changed and now that\NHino and Nagafuji were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made new artificial friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Hino and Nagafuji\Nwere at least entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But we weren't so close\NI'd go out of my way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to hang out with them now\Nthat our classes were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't keep up with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really hold onto relationships\Nand that might make me coldhearted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's how I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so very few strong relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that flow along with you\Ndown this river of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:59.43,OS,,0,0,0,,"When should I return the notes I borrowed?"\N"The next time we see each other is fine."\N"Thanks."\N"I haven't seen..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The longer you stay in this river of fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the more bonds weaken, and eventually break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi stopped showing up to class
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the following Monday after the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go have a peek?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's what Adachi's waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I go up there and a teacher spots us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you close with Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, she's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured. I saw you two talking all\Nthe time last year. Is she sick today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went to the same middle school\Nas Adachi, but she's totally changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I mean, she still didn't\Ntalk to anyone in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but she seemed even more guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if any of that has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, there's something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't feel so... standoffish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, she doesn't\Nseem so prickly anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, when I interact with Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't bother with the thorns\Nand just stiffens and curls up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's rejection wasn't even that strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't go check the second floor of the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Tarumi" "Incoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey... Um, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna hang out sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll try harder this time. I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so things don't end up as awkward as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't know if you need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Yeah, we're going to hang out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. How about next Saturday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Heck yeah! I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Miss... Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured this was a better attitude to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you prefer hanging out with someone calmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is worth looking into...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,At least she's decisive about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:13:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is paradise...\NHaving such a big bath is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer the one at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd call it being frugal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I like smaller houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see. Wanna trade homes then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... Yeah, that'd be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like anything would\Nchange here even if I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I'd let you touch\Nthem once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You like them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:14:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so generous, aren't I? But don't\Nmove your fingers around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's enough, tha--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are cute, Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really do like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen once we see each other?\NI probably shouldn't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that when I go out with Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're early!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Adachi's about the only person\Nwho'd rush over in a Chinese dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was I laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'm not late, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I just came too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so, uh... Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Oh, right. I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:16:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You always laughed like that, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shima, you've gotten sexier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't think of the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I wanted to say...\NYou've gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't think you need to\Npush this being super excited thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. At least half of it is genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:35.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Okonomiyaki{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this exhausting for your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.62,0:16:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think stuff like this\Nis important... Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hear you've been responsible lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom calls my mom sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They only talk to each other\Nsuper rarely, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They go so long without speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear that from\Nyou personally, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's partially the reason why\NI invited you out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, my goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a nicer way to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about our recent events while\Nmaking sure our {\i1}okonomiyaki {\i0}didn't burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru is surprisingly observant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were Adachi, I spaced out and\Nimagined she'd probably burn the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how much whatever Taru was\Nsaying wasn't getting through to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly am a coldhearted person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I was physically facing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,there was still a part of me\Nkeeping its distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say that you're my acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Acquaintance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:18:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That I've known for a while...\NAnd now I'm here in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I even saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where are we going next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's a little shop over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they sell random knickknacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, they have a lot of straps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we buy matching ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you like? I'll match mine\Nwith whatever one you pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you actually put it on your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that something to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling you'd lose it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean... You don't really\Nget attached to people or things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm worried that you\Nmight not take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your expression\Nis really vague right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Vague?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But whenever I see your profile with\Nsuch a vague expression on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you're actually thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Would it be possible to hang out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends again, Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why she invited me out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have located Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,S-See you later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru has always been like that, and in\Nthe past, I was able to keep up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I think that maybe\NI'm the odd one out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What even am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just you, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.\NYou actually can be useful at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks after our first term started...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:33.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,So, yesterday, I went to club\Nfor the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, I went to my classes,\Nbought bread at the student store,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.11,On Top,,0,0,0,,They were awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and ate lunch with my artificial friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:38.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's that third-year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just kept doing the same thing\Nover and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:40.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:43.53,On Top,,0,0,0,,Being in a club is sort of a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing that was different...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,..was Adachi wasn't in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,They're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:49.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,Relationships are so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, on our way home,\Nwanna get pancakes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Shi--?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After Sancho, and Taru,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this was the third time someone\Ncalled me since April started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.16,0:22:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the third time really is the charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it was finally Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:21.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 10: 'Cherry Blossoms and\NSpring and Spring and the Moon'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:24:06.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'The Moon and Determination,\NDetermination and Friends'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.80,0:23:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: New school term.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the same class as you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's act like we've never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.10,0:24:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lovely and mature, Miss Nagafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're oh so cute, Miss Hino.
